contents: input notifying: aController 	"The retrieved information has changed and its source must now be 	updated. The information can be a variety of things, depending on the 	list selections (such as templates for class or message definition, methods) 	or the user menu commands (such as definition, comment, hierarchy). 	Answer the result of updating the source."	| aString aText theClass |	aString := input asString.	aText := input asText.	editSelection == #editComment 		ifTrue: [theClass := self selectedClass.				theClass ifNil: [self inform: 'You must select a classbefore giving it a comment.'.				^ false].				theClass comment: aText. ^ true].	editSelection == #editMessageCategories 		ifTrue: [^ self changeMessageCategories: aString].	self inform:'You cannot change the current selection'.	^false